        {
            "title": "簡訊：國藥盈收雖齊升 首季現金流出續擴大",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"280\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Dipxa1AXqkZK6y7jgD1tBA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUzOA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/the_bamboo_works_186/4aabaea11fae4ec296b82206939a8c91\" width=\"500\"/></div></figure></div>",
