        {
            "title": "軟銀據悉尋求以OpenAI股份作抵押 獲得100億美元保證金貸款",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 知情人士稱，軟銀集團正尋求一筆100億美元的貸款，以所持美國人工智能(AI)巨頭OpenAI的股份作抵押。因大力進軍AI領域，這家日本企業集團正背上更多債務。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">知情人士透露，這筆期限兩年的保證金貸款將附帶一項選擇權，允許軟銀將借款期限再延長一年。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">軟銀的一位代表不予置評。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">隨著軟銀創始人孫正義通過大規模投資ChatGPT開發者OpenAI，尋求將自己定位為全球AI熱潮中的核心角色，該公司的債務負擔也日益加重。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-4e494611-2f64-3924-ab44-21ac451e9f53-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">3月時，標普將軟銀評級展望從穩定下調至負面，理由是該公司近期對OpenAI追加300億美元投資的計畫可能會損害其流動性及資產的信用質量。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">關於軟銀目前正在尋求的保證金貸款，目前尚未做出任何決定，具體細節可能仍會有變化。知情人士稱，討論內容包括初始利差可能在基準隔夜擔保融資利率(SOFR)基礎上加425個基點左右。按最新SOFR水平計算，相當於約7.88%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題SoftBank Seeks $10 Billion Margin Loan Backed by OpenAI Shares</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Min-Jeong Lee.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%BB%9F%E9%8A%80%E6%93%9A%E6%82%89%E5%B0%8B%E6%B1%82%E4%BB%A5openai%E8%82%A1%E4%BB%BD%E4%BD%9C%E6%8A%B5%E6%8A%BC-%E7%8D%B2%E5%BE%97100%E5%84%84%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E4%BF%9D%E8%AD%89%E9%87%91%E8%B2%B8%E6%AC%BE-010221613.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-23 09:50:05",
