        },
        {
            "title": "日本4月製造業PMI超預期;服務業拖累整體增長放緩",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/OpxJh5e.VfSl5wjWvpD8yA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEB1E0H5_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com- 週四公佈的採購經理人指數數據顯示,日本<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"製造業\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:製造業;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/製造業\">製造業</a>活動在4月以一年多來最快的速度擴張,有助於抵消服務業增長放緩的影響。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">標普全球日本製造業PMI初值從3月的51.6升至4月的54.9,超過51.1的預期。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">製造業產出指數從52.1攀升至55.4,創下自2014年2月以來產量增幅最大的紀錄,原因是企業在中東衝突可能導致供應中斷的擔憂下加快了生產。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">然而,整體私營部門增長放緩。綜合PMI初值從53.0降至52.4,顯示擴張速度為四個月來最慢,但仍高於區分增長與收縮的50門檻。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-9381fa96-1bc7-3c3a-9c85-ec5b085c96cf-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">服務業板塊表現落後,服務業PMI從53.4降至51.2,創下近一年來最弱讀數,原因是需求增長放緩。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">新業務在製造業訂單走強的支持下溫和上升,而出口增長則放緩至四個月低點。與此同時,成本壓力加劇,投入價格以2023年1月以來最快的速度上漲,主要受燃料和原材料成本上升推動。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">商業信心減弱至2020年8月以來的最低水平,反映出對中東衝突和潛在供應鏈中斷的不確定性。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC4%E6%9C%88%E8%A3%BD%E9%80%A0%E6%A5%ADpmi%E8%B6%85%E9%A0%90%E6%9C%9F-%E6%9C%8D%E5%8B%99%E6%A5%AD%E6%8B%96%E7%B4%AF%E6%95%B4%E9%AB%94%E5%A2%9E%E9%95%B7%E6%94%BE%E7%B7%A9-015956445.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-23 10:10:04",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "美伊緊張局勢持續,美股期貨下跌,儘管停火延長",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/a6RCAuwenlClVnuZ1wBDBw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEABU081_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com- 美國股指期貨在週三晚間小幅下跌,此前標普500指數和納斯達克指數升至歷史新高,儘管美國總統川普延長了停火協議,但美伊緊張局勢仍在持續。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">截至美國東部時間20:38(北京時間00:38),標普500指數期貨下跌0.3%至7,153.25點,納斯達克100指數期貨下跌0.1%至27,045.0點。道指期貨下跌0.5%至49,436.0點。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>伊朗在停火延長後於海峽扣押船隻</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在常規交易時段,標普500指數上漲1.1%,收於7,130點上方的歷史新高,而納斯達克綜合指數在科技股帶領下飆升1.6%至歷史新高。道瓊工業平均指數上漲0.7%。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-7e164885-3461-3792-b394-08553714c415-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在美國總統川普應巴基斯坦要求延長與伊朗的停火協議後,樂觀情緒推動了股市上漲。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此舉有助於緩解對局勢升級的即時擔憂,儘管伊朗的反應以及美國在霍爾木茲海峽(一條關鍵的石油運輸路線)附近持續的海軍封鎖仍存在不確定性。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">然而,在伊朗伊斯蘭革命衛隊扣押兩艘貨櫃船並向至少一艘其他船隻開火後,市場情緒轉為謹慎,伊朗指控這些船隻違反海事規則並試圖在未經授權的情況下通過海峽。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這一事件是伊朗自今年稍早與美國和以色列的衝突升級以來首次進行此類扣押,凸顯了停火協議的脆弱性。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">事件發生後,油價攀升至每桶100美元以上。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>企業財報提供支撐</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在值得關注的個股中,晶片製造商美光科技(NASDAQ:MU)創下歷史新高,而GE Vernova(NYSE:GEV)在上調營收展望後大漲。波音公司(NYSE:BA)因強勁的飛機需求而上漲,波士頓科學公司(NYSE:BSX)也在公布樂觀業績後上漲。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">盤後交易中,特斯拉(NASDAQ:TSLA)公布了喜憂參半的業績。這家電動汽車製造商報告營收約為224億美元,未達預期,儘管利潤和自由現金流超出預期。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span>特斯拉</span></span></span></span>股價在盤後交易中最初上漲,但隨後回落。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">預定於週四公布業績的公司包括霍尼韋爾國際(NASDAQ:HON)、美國運通(NYSE:AXP)、黑石集團(NYSE:BX)、<span><span>美國航空</span></span>(BMV:AAL)和洛克希德馬丁公司(NYSE:LMT)。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
